7:["$","div",null,{"className":"prose","children":[["$","h2",null,{"children":"Feature Analysis"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"Both Serpstat and Ubersuggest share a solid foundation of core features including Keyword Research, Rank Tracking, Site Audit, Backlink Analysis. Where Serpstat pulls ahead is with exclusive access to Api Access, which can be a deciding factor for teams that rely on this capability. On the other hand, Ubersuggest uniquely offers Ai Writing, giving it an edge for users who prioritize this area. \n\nLooking at user ratings, Serpstat holds an overall score of 7/10 and an ease of use score of 6/10, while Ubersuggest scores 6/10 overall and 8/10 for ease of use. These ratings reflect real user experiences and can indicate differences in usability, support quality, and overall satisfaction."}]]}]
8:["$","div",null,{"className":"prose","children":[["$","h2",null,{"children":"Pricing Breakdown"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"When it comes to pricing, Ubersuggest comes in at a lower starting price of $29/mo, while Serpstat begins at $69/mo. Ubersuggest stands out by offering a free plan, giving you a risk-free way to explore the platform. Serpstat requires a paid subscription from the start."}]]}]
