b:["$","div",null,{"className":"prose","children":[["$","h2",null,{"children":"Who Should Choose Which?"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"The ideal user for each platform differs considerably. Serpstat is best suited for SMBs, in house SEOs, budget teams, making it a strong choice if you fall into any of these categories. Ubersuggest, meanwhile, shines for beginners, solopreneurs, small businesses, which means it may be the better pick if your needs align with those use cases.\n\nFounded in 2013, Serpstat describes itself as \"Growth hacking SEO tool for keyword research, rank tracking, and site audit.\" Ubersuggest, established in 2017, positions itself as \"Neil Patel's affordable SEO tool for keyword ideas and site audits.\" Both platforms have been in the market for a similar duration, giving each ample time to refine their offerings and build a loyal user base."}]]}]
c:["$","div",null,{"className":"verdict-box","children":[["$","h2",null,{"children":"Our Verdict"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"After analyzing all the data, **Serpstat** comes out slightly ahead in this comparison, thanks to higher user ratings (7.0 vs 6.0). However, this does not mean Ubersuggest is a poor choice — far from it. Ubersuggest excels in its own right, particularly for beginners and solopreneurs.\n\nOur recommendation: if you value good value for comprehensive features, go with Serpstat. If very affordable with lifetime plan option matters more to you, Ubersuggest is the way to go. Either way, both are solid platforms that have earned their place in the market."}]]}]
